snippet.title: “She’s Untalented” Jason Mamoa speaks on Working with Amber Heard
snippet.description:
“She’s Untalented” Jason Mamoa speaks on Working with Amber Heard
According to Jason Momoa, Amber Heard was fired from Aquaman 2 for a reason. For quite some time, Jason Mamoa has been creating waves in the entertainment business. Indeed, since the release of Aquaman earlier this year, he has been the buzz of Hollywood, and he has been cast in a variety of roles in a number of films, causing us to speculate. Due to Aquaman's tremendous success soon after its release, the next time we see this heartthrob on the big screen will be in 2022.

💗 Hope you liked the video and would consider leaving a like and telling us what you thought in the comments!
